content.CONV_H_MISSION_4B:
[
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "It may seem like a strange question..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Do you know someone who is an expert in computer security?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": ":O"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "No, sorry."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "What happened?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "There is a guy who hacked me several times..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I have formatted the system but the guy keeps coming in"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "The last straw was that he discovered my bank password and stole money from me"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Uff ... That's very serious"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Have you called the police?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "No... the guy blackmails me saying that if I tell the police it will be much worse"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "he says he has friends like him, and they won't hesitate to come after me if I report him"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "What operating system do you use?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "The one almost everyone uses, Ellipse"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I would plan to change the operating system in your place... lately it has a reputation for being insecure"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Maybe that guy is bluffing and is just a kid using some code that he has found on the net"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I don't know if installing another operating system will solve the problem, but I guess I don't lose anything by trying"
  }
]

content.CONV_H_MISSION_4C:
[
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Hello it's me again"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "xDD"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Why don't you leave me alone?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Are you such an idiot that you still haven't figured out who I am?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I don't understand anything"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I know you?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Tell me who you are and why don't you stop hacking into my computer."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I am $NPC_IDX0"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Nothing?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "We worked together in the same company for 10 years."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Until you decided to spread the rumor that I hit my children and I don't know what other crazy things"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "You knew that when they were about to choose one of the two for the promotion, they weren't going to wait for everything to clear up"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Well, congratulations Mr. CEO, you also got me fired"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I don't know what you're talking about"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "We know each other very well and we both know it was you."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Do you have evidence of that?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Of course not"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "But I assure you that you will regret this"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "At the moment I have managed to access your bank account and have made some transfers"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I'm going to call the police"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I do not recommend it, I have found some documents on your computer that can get you in some trouble with the police"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Tell me what you want"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Don't worry, as soon as I finish the list I will send it to you."
  }
]

