    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I did not get to go up to the first floor, there was a huge noise with the fight and I left"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Our relationship is over. We will never speak again."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "But what...?"
  },
