    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Our company cannot be involved in any scandal, if they can prove that we have stolen the technology, we are going to have problems"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Technically... a person has found out, but if he knows what is good for him he will not say that it was me."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "What?? What do you mean technically? Who knows?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "My old co-worker on the project."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "He has deduced that it was me."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Are you telling me that the co-creator of the whole project knows that you just stole it from him?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "You just had to download the data remotely!"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "How did he find out?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Because I have deleted the project from the server :)"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Sorry, I can't believe what I'm reading."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Obviously everyone will find out if the files have been deleted."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Haha of course, the deletion has been my decision as revenge for those rats on the board of directors."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "And as far as I'm concerned, you guys are no better, so screw you."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "A bit naive of you to think that there will be no retaliation for this."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Are you sure? I think the following will happen."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "You're going to shut up your fucking mouth and you're going to pay me double what we agreed to."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I admit that was funny."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "So funny that I am the only person who can access the data in the backup."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Either you tell the police everything, you close the company and someone goes to jail with me. Surely investors have a lot to say about all this."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Get on with work."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "That seemed to me."
  }
]

