content.CONV_K_MISSION_3:
[
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "$NPC_IDX0 told me to meet without him, he has some things to do..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I don't think I have seen anyone with such eye bags."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Is he not sleeping or what?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I've tried talking to him but he gets defensive, and says he's fine, just a little stressed out from work."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "And how will he be when he is VERY stressed?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "It is clear that it is not because of work, something has happened recently, I would say that it is some problem of addiction to gambling or drugs perhaps"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "It is true that he is often absent at times without giving explanations."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "If he is not careful they will end up firing him, we will not be able to cover him much more."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Anyway, I think the documents for the meeting are on his computer, at the address $IP_LOCAL_IDX1"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I've already checked, the documents are not there"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Ah ok, sorry I have them here :)"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Okay, let's go"
  }
]

